<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about privoxy)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/privoxy.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jul 2017 11:30:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>通过privoxy实现http和https代理</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/tong-guo-privoxyshi-xian-httphe-httpsdai-li/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;有的时候为了完成某些测试，我们需要用到代理来更换IP地址，以下是可选的一种方法。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1、安装privoxy。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo apt install privoxy
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2、编辑配置文件。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo emacs /etc/privoxy/config
listen-address localhost:8118
forward-socks5 / 127.0.0.1:1080 .
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3、重启服务。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo service privoxy restart
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; sudo reboot
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>privoxy</category><category>proxy</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/tong-guo-privoxyshi-xian-httphe-httpsdai-li/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 03 Mar 2017 12:14:40 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>